OL,4,Cdies aged 71
OL,6,FSwansea City said they were "deeply
OL,7,Fsaddened" by the news of James'
OL,8,Fpassing in a statement.
OL,10,F"The thoughts of everyone at Swansea
OL,11,FCity are with Leighton's friends and
OL,12,Ffamily at this sad time," the
OL,13,Fstatement read.
OL,15,F"Swansea City will wear black armbands
OL,16,Fin Saturday's Championship fixture
OL,17,Fagainst Huddersfield Town as a mark of
OL,18,Frespect.
