OL,6,F"Swansea City Under-21s will also wear
OL,7,Fblack armbands in their home match
OL,8,Fagainst Bristol City on Saturday."
OL,10,FThe rugby club in his hometown,
OL,11,FGorseinon RFC, described him on X as
OL,12,F"a top quality sportsman", while
OL,13,Fadding that "Leighton was a true
OL,14,Ffriend of the club and will be sadly
OL,15,Fmissed by our members past and present.
OL,17,F"Our thoughts are with his family at
OL,18,Fthis time."
